{"tid":1176231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家咁多五毛借d椅勸退遊行，就知道西環瀨緊屎","createTime":"2019-05-29T05:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:45:23.000Z","uid":68329,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e49d8671fd2df6b9cd5bc7e25c11c2f9eb4e6da6","tid":1176231,"uid":68329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"咩俾外國利用<br />\n咩大劉都縮好多連登仔洩氣<br />\n<br />\n送中條例邊個推既？外國人推既？外國都係因為真香港人係咁向外宣傳而家先知先出聲<br />\n仆街政府不知幾想冇人知情況下偷偷地過！<br />\n<br />\n6月9號抗爭標語係還我大劉？熱烈歡迎大劉回家？<br />\n痴9左線？如果唔係為大劉，點解大劉縮沙會洩氣？<br />\n<br />\n好明顯，西環已經驚到瀨屎，唔理你係想和平定想衝，出黎人數多佢地就大檸樂，6月9號前一定會不停改改改改，千祈唔好信！回歸咁耐，邊單野係信者得救既？！<br />\n<br />\n你老母仆街五毛為左五毛埋沒良心，就黎推老母去做雞仲要幫手sell"},{"pid":"2adfad3e73870ae11f94fedbe61c53e4a4c9ab65","tid":1176231,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c380eda1d25166cd62c462ef3ad2363aa3e87f","tid":1176231,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"同飯民講 政府肯傾佢地就當成功爭取 打晒飛機咁"},{"pid":"21120478763c101fefd61fe757e6aa8cb85b1939","tid":1176231,"uid":238013,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"我又出嚟扮下五毛等你感覺良好先"},{"pid":"9047895765b745d4db7cefd74106ee127939e10b","tid":1176231,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08253ad3e57e20131d3d9520dc7f5acc0aa6ebe7","tid":1176231,"uid":62837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4c380eda1d25166cd62c462ef3ad2363aa3e87f","tid":1176231,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score